       <p>d.The Client confirms awareness of the risks involved in securities market investment and does not indemnify the Research Analyst against any direct or indirect loss.</p>
       <p>e. The Client shall not hold the RA liable for any investment losses resulting from implementation of research services.</p>
       <p>f. Understand that research services are non-binding recommendations, and not assurances or guarantees of returns.</p>
       <p>g. The client agrees that any future changes or updates made by him/her to any service shall be deemed covered under this agreement, and no separate agreement shall be required for the same. This agreement shall remain valid for the duration specified in the latest invoice.</p>
        <p class="section-title"><strong> 5. Declaration By Research Analyst </strong><br/></p>
        <p>a. It is duly registered with SEBI as an RA having Registration No.: {{ra_registration}} , Date of Registration: {{ra_reg_date}}
        </p>
        <p>b. It has registration and qualifications required to render the services contemplated under the RA Regulations, and the same are valid and subsisting.</p>
        <p>c. The services provided by the RA do not conflict with or violate any provision of law, rule, regulation, contract, or other instrument to which it is a party.</p>
        <p>d. The maximum fee that may be charged by the RA is <b> INR 1.51 lakhs per annum </b> per family of clients. All applicable taxes (GST, etc.) shall be borne by the Client only.</p>
        <p>e. The recommendations provided by the RA do not provide any assurance of returns.</p>
        <p>f. The RA is not engaged in any additional professional or business activities on a full-time or executive capacity that may interfere with or influence the independence of the research report and/or recommendations.</p>
        <p>g. No conflict of interest exists in recommendations provided. Independence and objectivity of views shall be maintained.</p>
        <p class="section-title"><strong>6. Risk Disclosure </strong><br/>
        The Client acknowledges and understands that the services provided by the Research Analyst involve inherent risks, and the Client agrees to bear full responsibility for any financial or other consequences arising from the use of these services. Investment in the market is always subject to market risk, and the following risks apply:
        </p>
        <p>a. Trading in equities, derivatives, and other securities are subject to market risks and there is no assurance or guarantee of returns.</p>
        <p>b. Past performance does not indicate future performance.</p>
        <p>c. Research recommendations may not always be profitable, as actual market movements may differ from anticipated trends.</p>
        <p>d. The Research Analyst is not responsible or liable for any losses resulting from research recommendations.</p>
        <p>e. Investments are subject to market risks; clients should read all related documents carefully before investing.</p>
        <p>f. Registration granted by SEBI, BASL, and certification from NISM do not guarantee the performance of the intermediary or provide any assurance of returns to investors.</p>
         <p class="section-title"><strong>7. Conflict Of Interest</strong><br/>
        The RA shall adhere to the applicable regulations/ circulars/directions specified by SEBI from time to time in relation to disclosure and mitigation of any actual or potential conflict of interest. Some disclosures are as follows:
        </p>
        <p>a. The Research Analyst or any of its officer/employee does not trade in securities which are subject matter of recommendation.</p>
        <p>b. There are no actual or potential conflicts of interest arising from any connection to or association with any issuer of products/securities, including any material information or facts that might compromise its objectivity or independence in the carrying on of Research Analyst services. Such conflict of interest shall be disclosed to the client as and when they arise.</p>
        <p>c. Research Analyst or its employee or its associates have not received any compensation from the company which is subject matter of recommendation.</p>
